<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>, uns hat
                                <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan>
<expan cert="unknown">F.</expan> Pawr, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger,
                        wie daz Üllein Dorn, <expan>H<ex>er</ex>man</expan> Schoffer und
                                <expan>W<ex>er</ex>nlein</expan> Schreck, die euch <expan>czu
                                versprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> steen, den
                            <expan>W<ex>er</ex>nlein</expan> Sneyder von Herlspach, des
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>gestoch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, geslagen
                        und gewundet <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und darczu auch niht sicher vor
                        in sey. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir mit
                            <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> die das getan
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> schicken wöllet, daz sie den
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan> sicher auf
                            <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> reht, als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und
                            <expan>hete<ex>n</ex></expan> sie <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> im icht
                            <expan>cze sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> wil
                        der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> von <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> armman in <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> irem
                                <expan>scheinbot<ex>en</ex></expan> etc.
                                <add><expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> etc.</add> ut in
                                <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan> post <expan>Barth<ex>olomei.</ex></expan>
</ab>
